title: Spacious Large Unit in a Side by Side Duplex Private Drive & Yard
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 302926525', 'Rent: $4,950 / Month', 'Beds: 4', 'Bath: 2.5', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Broker Fee: 1 Months Rent', 'Pet: No Pets', 'Rent Includes:: Water', 'Parking:: off-street parking', 'Renovated unit in a two-family (Side-by-Side House with Separated Outdoor space and Separate Driveways) feels like a single-family home.', '3 level living, with four bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, living room, dining room, kitchen with stainless steel appliances, sunroom, bonus room, and giant finished basement for a home office, gym, home theatre, game room, studio, etc.', 'Two decorative fireplaces, an in-unit washer and drier, tankless hot water, gas heat, plus central air conditioning with two zones.', 'Plenty of off-street parking and a private yard.', 'The owner pays for water and sewer.', 'Renter is responsible for gas and electricity.', 'No smoking allowed.', 'No pets.', 'Lot size: 0.27 Acres', 'Built-in 1950', 'Schools provided by the owner: Disclosure: We recommend contacting the local school district to confirm school assignments for this home Tenants/Tenant Agent to do Due Diligence', 'Elementary: Lowell', 'Middle: Watertown', 'High: Watertown', '1 Months Broker Fee.', 'Carlina Nabatoff', 'Text Friendly | 617-992-0978', 'The Abundant Group | A kw Cambridge Team', '**All Apartments Subject to Current Availability and Pricing.', 'Prices and Availability are subject to Change.', 'Pictures in the Advertising May NOT be of the actual unit but will represent the unit in its likeness.', 'A Keller Williams Realty Cambridge Team']
